20Bashir%20has%20applied%20for%20certification%20multiple%20times%20and%20fits%20all%20the%20criteria%20but%20has%20been%20repeatedly%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20still%2C%20to%20this%20day%2C%20being%20suppressed%20and%20being%20stifled%20in%20our%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20reap%20the%20same%20benefits%20as%20other%20content%20creators.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBashir%20estimates%20up%20to%2070%25%20of%20her%20current%20followers%20wouldn't%20move%20to%20Instagram%20or%20another%20platform%20if%20TikTok%20is%20banned%2C%20so%20despite%20its%20faults%2C%20she%20wants%20it%20to%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20love%20this%20app%2C%20we%20want%20this%20app%2C%20but%20the%20love%20isn't%20reciprocated%2C%26quot%3B%20Bashir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20in%20charge%20should%20remember%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20traditionally%20the%20ones%20that%20organize%2C%26quot%3B%20Bashir%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20will%20fight%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20TikTok%20for%20further%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblack-content-creators-could-be-most-affected-by-tiktok-ban-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714553975000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662f79e710dfcda409644a08%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblack-content-creators-could-be-most-affected-by-tiktok-ban-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Black%20creators%20spoke%20with%20Business%20Insider%20about%20why%20they%20fear%20a%20potential%20TikTok%20ban.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ldodgson%40insider.com%20(Lindsay%20Dodgson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblack-content-creators-could-be-most-affected-by-tiktok-ban-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%2