20Of%20Ms%20Gandhi%2C%20he%20says%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20can%20I%20say%20about%20someone%20I%20have%20never%20seen%2C%20never%20met%3F%20Dinesh%20Pratap%3Cem%3E%20ji%20%3C%2Fem%3Evisits%20us%20once%20a%20week.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20part%20of%20the%20village%2C%20his%20young%20caste%20fellow%2C%20Nishant%2C%20is%20studying%20to%20become%20a%20surgical%20assistant%2C%20even%20as%20he%20helps%20his%20elder%20brother%2C%20Chandan%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20little%20chemist%20shop.%20Their%20father%20left%20the%20village%2020%20years%20ago%20for%20Amritsar%2C%20where%20he%20worked%20with%20a%20goldsmith%2C%20to%20educate%20his%20six%20children%20-%20two%20boys%20and%20four%20girls.%20Six%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20returned%20with%20his%20family%20to%20the%20village%2C%20where%20he%20owns%20just%20half%20a%20bigha%20of%20land.%20The%20family%20has%20followed%20the%20electoral%20trajectory%20of%20other%20Pasis%20-%20first%20the%20Congress%2C%20then%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20and%20now%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Yadav%20Vote%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Yadavs%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20are%20divided%3B%20while%20most%20will%20vote%20for%20the%20Congress%20as%20it%20is%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%2C%20others%20will%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP.%20Rambahadur%20Yadav%20owns%20six%20bighas%20of%20land%20and%20has%20four%20children%20-%20his%20daughter%20is%20married%2C%20while%20his%20three%20sons%20are%20drivers%2C%20two%20in%20Raebareli%20and%20one%20in%20Mumbai.%20The%20earnings%20of%20the%20three%20sons%20maintain%20the%20household.%20Rambahadur%20says%20he%20will%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20adding%20it%20is%20because%20Ayushman%2C%20the%20government%20health%20scheme%2C%20enabled%20him%20to%20have%20two%20heart%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20Suraj%20Pal%20Yadav%2C%20it%20will%20be%20Congress%20again.%20His%20grandson%2C%20who%20is%20with%20him%2C%20is%20home%20from%20Surat%20during%20holidays%2C%20where%20he%20works%20in%20a%20dyeing%20unit%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20brother-in-law%20who%20is%20the%20supervisor%20there.%20%C2%A0He%20is%20just%20a%20teenager%20and%20had%20to%20discontinue%20his%20studies%20after%20Class%209%20as%20there%20was%20no%20money.%20He%20earns%20Rs%2015%2C000%20a%20month%20and%20sends%20back%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Yadavs%20of%20Johwa%20Sharqi%2C%20life%20has%20been%20hard%3A%2060%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20part%20of%20the%20village%20in%20which%20they%20lived%20was%20taken%20over%20by%20a%20rival%20caste%2C%20and%20they%20had%20to%20flee.%20Then%2C%20three%20decades%20back%2C%20they%20returned%20to%20rebuild%20their%20lives.%20Former%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20comes%20in%20for%20some%20praise%20from%20the%20community%20for%20the%20farm%20loan%20waivers%20he%20gave%20during%20his%20tenure%20in%20South%20Block.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMuslims%20Of%20Johwa%20Sharqi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslims%20are%20the%20third%20largest%20community%20here%20with%20close%20to%2080%20homes.%20Waris%20Ali%2C%20who%20has%20a%20poorly%20stocked%20grocer's%20shop%2C%20says%20the%20Muslims%20will%20vote%20for%20the%20Congress%20again.%20He%20has%2010%20bighas%20of%20land%2C%20but%20cannot%20grow%20anything%20there%20as%20it%20has%20been%20waterlogged%20ever%20since%20a%20canal%20was%20built%20through%20it.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20asked%20for%20compensation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20no%20one%20is%20willing%20to%20listen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20village%20official%20whom%20I%20had%20spoken%20to%20a%20while%20ago%20suddenly%20appears%20and%20listens%20to%20the%20exchange.%20Later%2C%20I%20ask%20him%20why%20Ali%20could%20not%20be%20compensated%20for%20his%20waterlogged%20land.%20Pat%20comes%20the%20answer%3A%20%26quot%3BHe's%20not%20really%20a%20farmer.%20He's%20a%20businessman.%20Didn't%20you%20see%20his%20shop%3F%20And%20he%20also%20makes%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20money%20selling%20fruits.%20He%20gets%20his%20free%20rations.%20What%20more%20does%20he%20want%3F%26quot%3B%20It%20is%20precisely%20this%20attitude%20that%20runs%20under%20the%20surface%20in%20terms%20of%20religious%20ties.%20There%20is%20no%20overt%20Hindu-Muslim%20tension%2C%20but%20the%20distrust%20-%20embedded%20in%20the%20soil%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20-%20remains.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Smita%20Gupta%20is%20a%20senior%20Delhi-based%20journalist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20of%20a%20multi-part%C2%A0series%C2%A0on%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20in%20which%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0Gupta%20profiles%20a%20few%20villages%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20each%20in%20a%20new%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20capturing%20the%20granular%20details%20of%20everyday%20life%20and%20the%20conversations%20of%20its%20residents.%20The%20first%20part%20can%20be%20read%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Flok-sabha-elections-hopes-aspirations-and-rivalries-in-aligarh-5518820%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20views%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714552740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F0np4b55o_rae-bareli_625x300_01_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Flok-sabha-elections-congress-gandhis-rae-bareli-old-loyalties-new-fault-lines-5563616%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Though%20neither%20the%20Congress%20nor%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20have%20announced%20their%20candidates%20for%20Raebareli%2C%20people%20here%20are%20making%20their%20own%20assumptions%2C%20based%20on%20their%20preferences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Flok-sabha-elections-congress-gandhis-rae-bareli-old-l