%20Smita%20Crishna%20(74)%20will%20oversee%20the%20other%2C%20as%20outlined%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rationale%20behind%20this%20split%2C%20according%20to%20the%20family's%20statement%2C%20is%20described%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bownership%20realignment%26quot%3B%20of%20their%20shareholdings%20in%20the%20Godrej%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20realignment%20has%20been%20arrived%20at%20in%20a%20respectful%20and%20mindful%20way%20to%20maintain%20harmony%20and%20to%20better%20align%20ownership%20in%20acknowledgement%20of%20the%20differing%20visions%20of%20the%20Godrej%20family%20members.%20This%20will%20help%20maximize%20strategic%20direction%2C%20focus%2C%20and%20agility%2C%20and%20will%20accelerate%20the%20process%20of%20creating%20long-term%20value%20for%20shareholders%20and%20all%20other%20stakeholders%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDivision%20of%20Assets%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20split%20entails%20dividing%20the%20conglomerate%20into%20two%20distinct%20entities%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGodrej%20Enterprises%20Group%20(GEG)%3A%20This%20arm%2C%20controlled%20by%20Jamshyd%20Godrej%20and%20his%20immediate%20family%2C%20encompasses%20Godrej%20%26amp%3B%20Boyce%20and%20its%20affiliates.%20GEG%20operates%20across%20multiple%20industries%2C%20including%20aerospace%2C%20aviation%2C%20defence%2C%20furniture%2C%20IT%20software%2C%20and%20real%20estate.%20Notably%2C%20it%20holds%20a%20significant%20land%20bank%2C%20including%20prime%20property%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGodrej%20Industries%20Group%20(GIG)%3A%20Led%20by%20Nadir%20Godrej%20and%20involving%20Adi%20Godrej%20and%20their%20immediate%20families%2C%20GIG%20comprises%20the%20listed%20companies%20within%20the%20conglomerate%2C%20such%20as%20Godrej%20Industries%2C%20Godrej%20Consumer%20Products%2C%20Godrej%20Properties%2C%20Godrej%20Agrovet%2C%20and%20Astec%20Lifesciences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETh