3EOn%20March%2023%2C%201994%2C%20Aeroflot%20Flight%20593%20from%20Moscow%20to%20Hong%20Kong%20crashed%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20all%2075%20people%20on%20board.%20The%2030-year-old%20catastrophic%20crash%20unfolded%20during%20the%20aircraft's%20first%20international%20flight.%20The%20cause%20of%20the%20accident%20was%20a%20mystery%20when%20accident%20investigators%20began%20their%20work%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20crash.%20But%20the%20true%20horror%20of%20what%20unfolded%20on%20the%20flight%20deck%20soon%20became%20clear%20as%20the%20investigation%20progressed.%20Although%20Aeroflot%20tried%20unsuccessfully%20to%20hide%20it%2C%20the%20answer%20stunned%20the%20world.%20At%20the%20moment%20of%20the%20loss%20of%20control%2C%20a%2015-year-old%20was%20flying%20the%20plane%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20a%20completely%20preventable%20tragedy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsimpleflying.com%2Faeroflot-flight-593%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESimple%20Flying%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20aircraft%20was%20carrying%2012%20flight%20crew%20and%2063%20passengers%20on%20board%2C%20including%20pilot%20Yaroslav%20Kudrinsky's%20two%20children.%20Halfway%20through%20the%20flight%2C%20the%20most%20experienced%20pilot%20Captain%20Andrey%20Danilov%20had%20left%20the%20cockpit%20to%20rest%2C%20leaving%20Mr%20Kudrinsky%20and%20first%20officer%20Igor%20Piskaryov%20in%20charge%20of%20flying%20the%20aircraft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plane%20was%20on%20autopilot%20and%20the%20course%20was%20set%20when%20Mr%20Kudrinsky%20opened%20the%20cockpit%20to%20some%20very%20important%20guests%20-%20his%20children.%20Keen%20to%20give%20them%20an%20unforgettable%20experience%2C%20he%20allowed%20each%20of%20them%20to%20take%20a%20seat%20in%20the%20Captain's%20seat%20and%20touch%20the%20controls%20to%20feel%20like%20they%20were%20flying%20the%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kudrinsky's%2012-year-old%20daughter%20Yana%20had%20her%20turn%20first%20without%20any%20complications.%20Her%20father%20even%20adjusted%20the%20autopilot%20to%20make%20her%20think%20she%20was%20actually%20steering%20the%20aircraft.%20She%20was%20followed%20by%20Mr%20Kudrinsky's%2016-year-old%20son%20Edgar.%20Once%20again%2C%20the%20pilot%20manipulated%20the%20controls%20slightly%20to%20give%20his%20son%20a%20taste%20of%20flying%20the%20plane%2C%20but%20in%20excitement%2C%20the%20boy%20pushed%20hard%20on%20the%20control%20column%2C%20which%20disengaged%20the%20autopilot%20control%20of%20the%20aircraft%2C%20leaving%20the%2016-year-old%20partially%20in%20control.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20clearly%20a%20situation%20that%20the%20experienced%20Russian%20pilot%20should%20have%20seen%20coming.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fadmiralcloudberg.medium.com%2Ffathers-and-sons-the-crash-of-aeroflot-flight-593-fc4947bdb1f1%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMedium%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20silent%20warning%20appeared%20on%20the%20flight%20deck%20but%20was%20missed%20before%20both%20of%20the%20pilots%20noticed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2015-year-old%20actions%20eventually%20caused%20the%20plane%20to%20veer%20sharply.%20From%20there%20the%20pilots%20attempted%20to%20regain%20control%20of%20the%20aircraft%2C%20successfully%20pulling%20the%20plane%20out%20of%20a%20dive%20but%20overcorrecting%20until%20the%20flight%20was%20climbing%20almost%20vertically%2C%20stalling%20it.%20This%20resulted%20in%20the%20plane%20spinning%20and%20dropping%20back%20down%20to%20the%20ground.%20While%20the%20pilots%20were%20able%20to%20level%20out%20the%20wings%20of%20the%20plane%20they%20had%20lost%20too%20much%20altitude%20by%20that%20point%20and%20crashed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbinance-founder-changpeng-zhao-becomes-worlds-richest-prisoner-after-receiving-4-month-sentence-5562760%5C%22%3EBinance%20Founder%20Changpeng%20Zhao%20Becomes%20World's%20Richest%20Prisoner%20After%20Receiving%204-Month%20Sentence%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20black%20box%20recording%20of%20the%20plane's%20final%20moments%20was%20discovered%20as%20part%20of%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20crash.%20It%20revealed%20that%20in%20the%20final%20moments%2C%20Mr%20Kudrinsky%20was%20shouting%20at%20his%20son%20to%20get%20away%20from%20the%20controls.%20%26quot%3BEldar%2C%20get%20away.%20Go%20to%20the%20back%2C%20go%20to%20the%20back%20Eldar!%20You%20see%20the%20danger%20don't%20you%3F%20Go%20away%2C%20go%20away%20Eldar!%20Go%20away%2C%20go%20away.%20I%20tell%20you%20to%20go%20away!%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20chaos%2C%20Mr%20Kudrinsky%20struggled%20to%20regain%20control%20of%20the%20plane%2C%20but%20it%20was%20too%20late.%20%26quot%3BGet%20out%20now%2C%20all%20is%20normal.%20Pull%20up%20gently.%20Gently!%20Gently%20I%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20But%20the%20aircraft%20plummeted%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20crashing%20in%20the%20Kuznetsk%20Alatau%20Mountain%20range%20of%20southern%20Russia%20at%20a%20speed%20of%20some%20160mph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EMedium%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20investigations%20found%20no%20evidence%20of%20technical%20failure%2C%20concluding%20the%20crash%20was%20most%20likely%20caused%20by%20the%20children%20being%20allowed%20to%20take%20control%20of%20the%20flight.%20The%20aircraft%20was%20completely%20destroyed%2C%20killing%20everyone%20onboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714551420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fdka7aitg_aeroflot-flight-593_625x300_01_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Faeroflot-flight-593-how-a-childs-cockpit-visit-caused-deadly-crash-in-1994-5563564%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20March%2023%2C%201994%2C%20Aeroflot%20Flight%20593%20from%20Moscow%20to%20Hong%20Kong%20crashed%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20all%2075%20people%20on%20board.%22%2C%22a