l%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223-Year-Old%20Thought%20There%20Were%20%26quot%3BMonsters%26quot%3B%20In%20Room%2C%20Beekeeper%20Discovers...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%203-year-old%20Saylor%20Class%20complained%20about%20monsters%20in%20her%20bedroom%2C%20her%20parents%20dismissed%20it%20as%20a%20figment%20of%20a%20child's%20vivid%20imagination.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68924955%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported%20that%20their%20perspective%20soon%20shifted%20when%20a%20beekeeper%20found%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20honeybees%20above%20the%20girl's%20bedroom.%20Saylor%20had%20been%20expressing%20concerns%20about%20%26quot%3Bmonsters%20in%20the%20wall%26quot%3B%20of%20her%20room%20at%20their%20farmhouse%20in%20Charlotte%2C%20North%20Carolina.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20mother%2C%20Ashley%20Massis%20Class%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20initially%20didn't%20pay%20much%20attention%20to%20it%2C%20considering%20they%20recently%20watched%20the%20Pixar%20movie%2C%20Monsters%2C%20Inc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20even%20gave%20her%20a%20bottle%20of%20water%20and%20said%20it%20was%20monster%20spray%20so%20that%20she%20could%20spray%20away%20any%20of%20the%20monsters%20at%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20Massis%20Class%2C%20a%20home%20designer%20told%20the%20BBC.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20trick%20didn't%20work%2C%20in%20the%20following%20months%2C%20Saylor%20grew%20adamant%20about%20something%20being%20inside%20her%20closet.%20Soon%2C%20her%20mother%20started%20connecting%20the%20dots%20and%20she%20observed%20bees%20gathering%20in%20groups%20in%20her%20attic%20and%20chimney%20outside%20their%20century-old%20residence.%20She%20figured%20Saylor%20must%20hear%20the%20buzzing%20noise%20near%20her%20bedroom%20ceiling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Class%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20pest%20control%20company%2C%20which%20discovered%20the%20insects%20were%20honeybees%2C%20a%20sp