0defence%20volunteers%26quot%3B%20and%20disarming%20them%20would%20put%20their%20village%20at%20risk%20of%20attack%20by%20armed%20men%20from%20nearby%20hills%2C%20amid%20the%20ethnic%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20of%20the%20incident%20that%20happened%20on%20Tuesday%20show%20the%20soldiers%20being%20pushed%20around%20by%20the%20women%2C%20who%20stood%20in%20front%20of%20an%20armoured%20mine-proof%20vehicle%20and%20stopped%20it%20from%20leaving%20the%20area%20with%20the%20confiscated%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurrounded%20by%20shouting%20and%20yelling%20protesters%2C%20the%20soldiers%20fired%20several%20rounds%20in%20the%20air%20to%20disperse%20the%20crowd.%20But%20it%20had%20little%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20go%20anywhere%2C%20stand%20here%2C%20stand%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20elderly%20woman%20is%20heard%20saying%20to%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20don't%20you%20take%20guns%20from%20everyone%2C%20why%20only%20from%20us%3F%26quot%3B%20another%20woman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Manipur%20Police%20team%20soon%20reached%20the%20spot%20and%20negotiated%20with%20the%20protesters%2C%20following%20which%20the%20army%20and%20the%20police%20team%20drove%20out%20of%20the%20area%20carrying%20the%20confiscated%20weapons%2C%20sources%20said.%20Even%20then%2C%20the%20protesters%20blocked%20the%20road%20with%20an%20abandoned%2C%20junked%20car%2C%20which%20the%20army%20truck%20hit%20and%20dragged%20on%20before%20it%20peeled%20off%20from%20the%20front%20bumper%20of%20the%20armoured%20military%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hill-dominated%20Kuki%20tribes%20and%20the%20valley-dominant%20Meiteis%20have%20been%20fighting%20since%20May%202023%20over%20cataclysmic%20disagreements%20on%20sharing%20land%2C%20resources%2C%20affirmative%20action%20policies%2C%20and%20political%20representation%2C%20mainly%20with%20the%20'general'%20category%20Meiteis%20seeking%20to%20be%20included%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20top%20factor%2C%20the%20state%20government%20says%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20crisis%20was%20its%20'war%20on%20drugs'%20campaign%20that%20ended%20up%20snatching%20food%20from%20the%20mouth%20of%20powerful%2C%20internationally-linked%20drug%20traffickers.%20The%20Kuki%20tribes%20call%20this%20a%20big%20lie%20for%20the%20Meiteis%20to%20grab%20their%20lands%2C%20as%20studies%20have%20shown%20poppy%20cultivation%20that%20provides%20fast%2C%20huge%20sums%20is%20linked%20to%20poverty%20and%20underdevelopment%20in%20the%20hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bneutral%26quot%3B%20central%20forces%20-%20according%20to%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20-%20such%20as%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force%2C%20and%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20are%20guarding%20sensitive%20areas%20in%20Manipur%20where%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20settlements%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20also%20hundreds%20of%20armed%20people%20in%20both%20communities%20who%20call%20themselves%20%26quot%3Bvillage%20defence%20volunteers%26quot%3B%20who%20may%20need%20to%20be%20disarmed%20simultaneously%20due%20to%20mutual%20distrust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20definition%20of%20the%20belligerents%20in%20Manipur%20has%20become%20the%20most%20controversial%20since%20nothing%20stops%20the%20%26quot%3Bvolunteers%26quot%3B%20from%20shooting%20others%20under%20the%20insurance%20provided%20by%20the%20%26quot%3Bin%20self-defence%26quot%3B%20claim.%20A%20similarity%20between%20the%20%26quot%3Bvillage%20defence%20volunteers%26quot%3B%20of%20both%20sides%20is%20they%20are%20well-armed%20and%20well-equipped%20with%20modern%20battle%20gear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20a%20Kuki%20group%20spearheading%20the%20call%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur%20had%20asked%20members%20of%20their%20tribes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-wont-deposit-licenced-arms-need-for-defence-kuki-zo-group-itlf-in-manipur-ahead-of-elections-5316414%5C%22%3Enot%20to%20give%20their%20licenced%20guns%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20police%20stations%20for%20safe-keeping%2C%20citing%20safety%20concerns%20amid%20the%20ethnic%20tensions%20with%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders'%20Forum%20(ITLF)%20in%20a%20statement%20had%20said%20licenced%20guns%20submitted%20last%20year%20have%20not%20been%20returned%20yet.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20every%20available%20weapon%20to%20defend%20our%20'right%20to%20life'%20and%20our%20land...%26quot%3B%20the%20ITLF%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20forces%20have%20frequently%20recovered%20Russian-origin%20AK%20and%20US-origin%20M%20series%20assault%20rifles%2C%20and%20gun%20models%20commonly%20used%20by%20both%20the%20junta's%20army%20and%20pro-democracy%20insurgents%20in%20neighbouring%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20210%20have%20died%20in%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%3B%20nearly%2050%2C000%20internally%20displaced%20people%20are%20still%20living%20in%20relief%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714550160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fsvlsgd1_manipur-army_625x300_01_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-high-drama-as-soldiers-fire-in-air-to-disperse-protesters-in-manipurs-bishnupur-5563475%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20army%20patrol%20that%20found%2011%20armed%20men%20in%20police%20uniform%20in%20Manipur's%20Bishnupur%20district%20was%20surrounded%20by%20a%20group%20of%20women%20protesters%20after%20the%20soldiers%20detained%20the%20men%20and%20seized%20their%20weapons%2C%20the%20police%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-high-drama-as-soldiers-fire-in-air-to-disperse-protesters-in-manipurs-bishnupur-5563475%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-n