20district%20in%20a%20manner%20far%20less%20intent%20on%20accuracy%20of%20detailing%20than%20on%20the%20overall%20effect%20of%20the%20enterprise.%20The%20show%20has%20passages%20of%20effulgent%20beauty.%20It%20also%20occasionally%20slides%20into%20tonally%20static%2C%20cinematically%20sterile%20stretches.%20But%20in%20the%20ultimate%20analysis%2C%20its%20strengths%20far%20outnumber%20its%20downsides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhansali%20is%20the%20creator%2C%20co-writer%20(with%20Vibhu%20Puri)%2C%20editor%20and%20music%20director%20of%20the%20extravagant%20eight-episode%20Netflix%20show%20that%20economizes%20on%20nothing%20at%20all.%20It%20is%20filmed%20all%20the%20way%20like%20the%20widescreen%20spectacle%20that%20it%20is%20intended%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20an%20original%20concept%20by%20Moin%20Beg%2C%20%3Ci%3EHeeramandi%3A%20The%20Diamond%20Bazaar%3C%2Fi%3E%20places%20the%20daily%20struggles%20of%20the%20fabled%20but%20exploited%20courtesans%20of%20Lahore%20alongside%20a%20rapidly%20escalating%20war%20for%20independence%20waged%20by%20a%20band%20of%20underground%20rebels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhansali%20tempers%20his%20maximalist%20methods%20with%20restraint.%20The%20series%20is%20a%20celebration%20of%20as%20well%20as%20a%20lament%20for%20a%20house%20of%20spirited%20courtesans%20yearning%20for%20dignity%20and%20liberty%20in%20the%20tumultuous%20final%20years%20of%20the%20British%20Raj%2C%20an%20era%20marked%20by%20the%20rapidly%20declining%20clout%20of%20the%20nawabs%20who%20were%20the%20chief%20patrons%20of%20the%20nautch%20girls%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsharmin-segal-lilly-singh-tesher-at-sanjay-leela-bhansalis-heeramandi-premiere-in-los-angeles-5558309%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EHeeramandi%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhansali%20draws%20the%20very%20best%20out%20of%20the%20six%20principal%20members%20of%20the%20cast%20-%20Manisha%20Koirala%2C%20Sonakshi%20Sinha%2C%20Aditi%20Rao%20Hydari%2C%20Richa%20Chadha%2C%20Sanjeeda%20Sheikh%20and%20Sharmin%20Segal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManisha%20Koirala%2C%20returning%20to%20a%20Bhansali%20project%2028%20years%20after%20%3Ci%3EKhamoshi%3A%20The%20Musical%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20Sonakshi%20Sinha%2C%20coming%20off%20the%20triumph%20of%20%3Ci%3EDahaad%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20embody%20two%20feisty%20women%20who%20denote%20the%20two%20principal%20poles%20of%20the%20a%20battle%20to%20control%20%3Ci%3EHeeramandi%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20is%20Aditi%20Rao%20Hydari%2C%20cast%20as%20an%20epitome%20of%20sedate%20grace%20and%20refinement%2C%20who%20gets%20a%20wider%20emotional%20spectrum%20to%20straddle.%20Sharmin%20Segal%2C%20playing%20an%20innocent%20but%20gifted%20young%20woman%20who%20wants%20to%20escape%20her%20destiny%2C%20has%20her%20moments%2C%20as%20does%20Sanjeeda%20Sheikh%20as%20a%20scarred%20woman%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20the%20bitter%20power%20struggle%20between%20forces%20much%20stronger%20than%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhansali%20is%20just%20as%20impressive%20in%20the%20way%20he%20harnesses%20the%20potential%20of%20the%20supporting%20actresses%20-%20notably%20Farida%20Jalal%2C%20Nivedita%20Bhargava%2C%20Jayati%20Bhatia%20and%20Shruti%20Sharma%20-%20to%20conjure%20up%20a%20sophisticated%2C%20if%20self-consciously%20stylised%2C%20portrait%20of%20a%20tumultuous%20time%20and%20a%20unique%20culture%20trapped%20caught%20in%20a%20maelstrom%20triggered%20by%20the%20vagaries%20of%20history%20and%20the%20myopia%20of%20self-serving%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20male%20cast%20-%20the%20actors%20play%20marginal%20figures%20who%20call%20the%20shots%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20courtesans%20or%20control%20the%20law-and-order%20machinery%20in%20the%20city%20-%20is%20far%20less%20effective.%20It%20includes%20Fardeen%20Khan%2C%20making%20a%20comeback%20after%20a%2014-year%20hiatus%2C%20and%20Shekhar%20Suman%2C%20who%2C%20too%2C%20has%20been%20missing%20from%20the%20screen%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20roles%20that%20Khan%20and%20Suman%20play%20-%20nawabs%20who%20have%20the%20%3Ci%3Etawaif%3C%2Fi%3Es%20of%20%3Ci%3EHeeramandi%3C%2Fi%3E%20as%20mistresses%20in%20a%20give-and-take%20relationship%20teetering%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20desire%20and%20distrust%20-%20are%20peripheral%20to%20the%20larger%20drama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20other%20male%20actors%20-%20Taha%20Shah%2C%20playing%20a%20well-connected%20and%20strategically%20pliant%20aristocrat's%20London-returned%20son%20who%20rebels%20against%20his%20father%20and%20the%20British%2C%20Jason%20Shah%20as%20a%20brutal%20British%20police%20officer%20and%20Indresh%20Malik%20as%20a%20foppish%2C%20wily%20mediator%20between%20the%20nautch%20girls%20and%20their%20fickle%20benefactors%20-%20are%20accorded%20greater%20play.%20They%20make%20the%20most%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20%3Ci%3EHeeramandi%3C%2Fi%3E's%20patrons%20(played%20by%20Adhyayan%20Suman%2C%20who%20is%20also%20cast%20as%20the%20younger%20avatar%20of%20the%20character%20essayed%20by%20Shekhar%20Suman)%2C%20demonstrates%20that%20the%20attention%20and%20riches%20that%20a%20debauched%20nawab%20showers%20on%20a%20tawaif%2C%20Lajjo%20(Richa%20Chadha)%2C%20are%20not%20permanent.%20They%20are%20part%20of%20an%20easy%20to%20violate%20Faustian%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20just%20devious%20outsiders%20who%20cause%20misery.%20The%20nautch%20girls%20themselves%20are%20equally%20capable%20of%20inflicting%20pain%20on%20each%20other%20with%20bursts%20of%20envy%20and%20acts%20of%20betrayal%20that%20stem%20from%20the%20need%20for%20acceptance%20and%20self-assertion.%20The%20%3Ci%3EHeeramandi%3C%2Fi%3E%20courtesans%20are%20a%20closely-knit%20community%20-%20most%20of%20them%20are%20related%20by%20blood%20-%20but%20that%20does%20not%20stop%20them%20from%20ceaselessly%20exchanging%20verbal%20and%20psychological%20barbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FWvzZYynDkwA%3Fsi%3DskG4F_LcEqYaUDka%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20series%20plays%20out%20predominantly%20in%20two%20mansions%20that%20stand%20opposite%20each%20other%20in%20the%20disreputable%20neighbourhood%20frequented%20by%20the%20powerful%20and%20the%20wealthy.%20One%20is%20Shahi%20Mahal%20(which%20translates%20to%20royal%20palace)%2C%20where%20a%20seasoned%20Mallikajaan%20(Manisha%20Koirala)%20is%20the%20undisputed%20queen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%2C%20Khwabgah%20(meaning%20%26quot%3Bhouse%20of%20dreams%26quot%3B)%2C%20is%20a%20much-coveted%20mansion%20into%20which%20the%20younger%20Fareedan%20(Sonakshi%20Sinha)%20moves%20after%20relocating%20from%20Benaras.%20Fareedan%2C%20the%20only%20daughter%20of%20Mallika's%20dead%20elder%20sister%2C%20has%20a%20score%20to%20settle%20with%20the%20denizens%20of%20Shahi%20Mahal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelusions%20of%20royalty%20and%20the%20lure%20of%20dreams%20sustain%20Mallikajaan%20and%20her%20likes.%20Dreams%2C%20as%20one%20of%20the%20women%20says%2C%20is%20their%20worst%20enemy.%20We%20can%20only%20see%20them%20but%20never%20realise%20them%2C%20she%20adds.%20It%20is%20the%20courtesans'%20perennial%20oscillation%20between%20hope%20and%20despair%20that%20lies%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20drama%20of%20their%20unstable%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EHeeramandi%3A%20The%20Diamond%20Bazaar%3C%2Fi%3E%20sustains%20its%20spotlight%20on%20the%20women%20even%20as%20it%20liberally%20sprinkles%20its%20sweeping%2C%20overflowing%20canvas%20with%20intimate%20moments%20of%20love%2C%20jealousy%2C%20deceit%20and%20rebellion%20and%20with%20unfolding%20processions%2C%20street%20clashes%20and%20cases%20of%20custodial%20torture%20that%20leave%20a%20trail%20of%20blood%20and%20unspeakable%20horrors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20once%20seductive%20and%20sad%2C%20poignant%20and%20prevailing%2C%20the%20tawaifs%20dwell%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Lahore%20but%20are%20doomed%20to%20languish%20as%20dispensable%20objects%20of%20fancy%20on%20the%20fringes%20of%20a%20society%20controlled%20by%20nawabs%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20oblivion%20and%20ruthless%20British%20officials%20desperately%20clinging%20on%20to%20their%20authority%20on%20an%20increasingly%20restless%20colonised%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dice%20is%20loaded%20against%20the%20courtesans%2C%20but%20they%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20emotionally%20control%20the%20moneyed%20men%20on%20whom%20they%20depend%20for%20their%20upkeep.%20But%20how%20long%20can%20they%20protect%20their%20shaky%20turf%20and%20keep%20the%20nawabs%20in%20their%20thrall%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20rumblings%20of%20the%20swadeshi%20movement%20spill%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmeet-aditi-rao-hydari-and-sonakshi-sinha-outside-bhansaliverse-pic-courtesy-siddharth-5550657%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EHeeramandi%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20Bibbojaan%20(Aditi%20Rao%20Hydari)%20and%20Alamzeb%20(Sharmin%20Segal)%2C%20Mallika's%20two%20daughters%2C%20are%20drawn%20into%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20one%20directly%2C%20the%20other%20inadvertently%20-%20the%20courtesans%20are%20caught%20in%20a%20cleft%20stick.%20They%20can%20either%20side%20with%20the%20nawabs%20who%20lack%20the%20courage%20to%20resist%20the%20British%20or%20throw%20their%20lot%20with%20the%20freedom%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ornately%20mounted%20%3Ci%3EHeeramandi%3C%2Fi%3E%20might%20at%20first%20flush%20appear%20to%20be%20a%20conventional%20SLB%20endeavour.%20It%20presses%20pretty%20images%20couched%20in%20music%20and%20poetry%20into%20the%20service%20of%20an%20account%20of%20an%20obscure%20and%20fictionalised%20chapter%20of%20the%20subcontinent's%20history.%20That%20it%20does%20so%20with%20consistent%20competence%20is%20only%20to%20be%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cinematography%20is%20credited%20to%20four%20DoPs%20-%20Bhansali's%20frequent%20collaborator%20Sudeep%20Chatterjee%20along%20with%20Mahesh%20Limaye%2C%20Huenstang%20Mohapatra%20and%20Ragul%20Dharuman%20-%20and%20the%20production%20design%20is%20by%20Subrata%20Chakraborty%20and%20Amit%20Ray.%20Both%20teams%20of%20technicians%20make%20flawless%20contributions%20to%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%2C%20however%2C%20more%20to%20the%20series%20than%20the%20blindingly%2C%20and%20distractingly%2C%20sumptuous%20means%20that%20Bhansali%20employs.%20There%20is%20a%20significant%20takeaway%20from%20the%20way%20%3Ci%3EHeeramandi%3A%20The%20Diamond%20Bazaar%3C%2Fi%3E%20frames%20the%20fight%20for%20India's%20independence%20as%20a%20movement%20that%20defied%20the%20Crown's%20divide%20and%20rule%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindus%20and%20Muslims%20walk%20shoulder%20to%20shoulder%20as%20they%20plot%20strikes%20against%20the%20British.%20Religious%20identities%20do%20not%20divide%20the%20fighters.%20Their%20commitment%20to%20%3Ci%3Eazaadi%3C%2Fi%3E%20unites%20them.%20In%20the%20climate%20that%20obtains%20in%20today's%20India%2C%20the%20espousal%20of%20the%20subcontinent's%20entrenched%20syncretism%20is%20a%20noteworthy%20thematic%20strand%20that%20should%20not%20be%20lost%20in%20the%20hypnotic%20glow%20of%20the%20glitzy%20%3Ci%3EHeeramandi%3C%2Fi%3E%20universe%20that%20Bhansali%20conjures%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EHeeramandi%3A%20The%20Diamond%20Bazaar%3C%2Fi%3E%20isn't%20all%20pomp%20and%20show.%20Both%20nostalgic%20and%20elegiac%2C%20it%20contains%20a%20core%20that%20is%20worth%20more%20than%20all%20the%20glitter%20and%20glory%20of%20its%20packaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714549140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fl9e35u08_-herrmandi_625x300_01_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fheeramandi-the-diamond-bazaar-review-theres-more-than-the-blindingly-sumptuous-means-sanjay-leela-bhansali-employs-3-stars-5563342%22%2C%22s