dian%20cricketer%20Rohan%20Gavaskar%20and%20opener%20Virender%20Sehwag%20have%20expressed%20dismay%20over%20Singh's%20omission%2C%20questioning%20the%20selection%20process%20and%20yardstick.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Fif-ipl-is-the-metric-where-has-mohammed-siraj-picked-wickets-debate-ignites-over-rinku-singhs-exclusion-from-indias-t20-world-cup-squad%2Farticleshow%2F109749293.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20Facts%20About%20Adi%20And%20Nadir%20Godrej%2C%20Owners%20Of%20Godrej%20Industries%20After%20Split%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Godrej%20Group%2C%20known%20for%20its%20diverse%20business%20ventures%2C%20has%20announced%20the%20division%20of%20their%20conglomerate.%20In%20an%20ownership%20redistribution%2C%C2%A0the%20billion-dollar%20venture%20will%20now%20be%20split%C2%A0into%20two%20branches%20of%20the%20family.%20Adi%20and%20Nadir%20Godrej%20will%20maintain%20control%20of%20Godrej%20Industries%2C%20which%20includes%20five%20listed%20firms.%C2%A0Their%20cousins%20Jamshyd%20Godrej%20and%20Smita%20Crishna%20will%20inherit%20Godrej%20%26amp%3B%20Boyce%C2%A0along%20with%20its%C2%A0affiliates%20and%20substantial%20real%20estate%20assets%2C%20including%20prime%20property%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWho%20is%20Adi%20Godrej%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Adi%20Godrej%2C%2082%2C%20is%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20%245.7%20billion%20revenue%20Godrej%20Group%2C%20a%20renowned%20consumer-goods%20giant%20established%20127%20years%20ago%20by%20lawyer%20Ardeshir%20Godrej%2C%20who%20transitioned%20from%20law%20to%20lock-making%20in%201897.%20Today%2C%20the%20Godrej%20Group%20is%20trusted%20by%201.2%20billion%20consumers%20worldwide%20across%20various%20industries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20His%20leadership%20extends%20to%C2%A0other%C2%A0major%20group%20companies%C2%A0such%C2%A0as%20Godrej%20Consumer%20Products%2C%20chaired%20by%20his%20daughter%20Nisaba%2C%20and%20Godrej%20Properties%2C%20managed%20by%20his%20son%20Pirojsha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Adi%20Godrej%20holds%20a%C2%A0Bachelor's%C2%A0and%20a%C2%A0Master's%C2%A0degree%20from%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(MIT)%20Sloan%20School%20of%20Management%2C%20where%20he%20is%20currently%20also%20a%20part%20of%20the%C2%A0Dean's%C2%A0Advisory%20Council.%C2%A0He%20is%20also%20on%20the%20Board%20of%20Governors%20of%20the%20Narsee%20Monjee%20Institute%20of%20Management%C2%A0Studies%2C%C2%A0and%C2%A0on%C2%A0the%20Wharton%20Asian%20Executive%20Board.%C2%A0In%20addition%2C%20Adi%20Godrej%20is%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Indian%20School%20of%20Business%20and%20has%20been%20President%20of%20the%20Confederation%20of%20Indian%20Industry.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20He%20has%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%243.8%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes.%C2%A0He%20is%20also%20a%20patron%20of%20the%20Himalayan%20Club.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Adi%20Godrej%20has%20been%20honoured%20with%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Award%20in%202002%20and%20the%20Padma%20Bhushan%2C%20the%20third-highest%20civilian%20award%2C%20in%202013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWho%20is%20Nadir%20Godrej%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Nadir%20Godrej%2C%2073%2C%20is%20the%20younger%20sibling%20of%20Adi%20Godrej.%20He%20holds%20a%20one-fifth%20share%20in%20the%20assets%20of%20the%20Godrej%20Group.%20He%C2%A0is%20currently%20serving%C2%A0as%20the%20chairman%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20Godrej%20Industries%20and%20also%20chairs%20the%20agribusiness%20unit%20Godrej%20Agrovet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Nadir%20Godrej%20joined%20the%20family%20enterprise%20over%20four%20decades%20ago.%20He%20has%20been%20to%20MIT%20and%C2%A0also%C2%A0has%20a%20Master%20of%20Science%20degree%20from%20Stanford%20University%20and%20an%20MBA%20from%20Harvard%20Business%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20He%C2%A0serves%20as%C2%A0a%20non-executive%20director%20for%20several%20companies%2C%20including%20Godrej%20%26amp%3B%20Boyce%20Co%20Ltd%2C%20Godrej%20Consumer%20Products%20Ltd%2C%20Indian%20Hotels%20Co%20Ltd%2C%20and%20Mahindra%20%26amp%3B%20Mahindra%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Nadir%20Godrej%20has%20been%20honoured%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98Chevalier%20de%20l'Ordre%20National%20du%20M%C3%A9rite'%20and%20%E2%80%98Chevalier%20de%20la%20L%C3%A9gion%20d'Honneur'%20by%20the%20French%20Government.%20He%20also%20received%20the%20Global%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%2C%20OTAI%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%2C%20Chemtech%20CEW%20Leadership%20%26amp%3B%20Excellence%20Award%2C%20and%20Chemexcil%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%20in%202012%20and%202013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Nadir%20Godrej%20is%20also%20a%20poet%20and%20has%20authored%20two%20poetry%20collections%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%E2%80%98Life%20and%20Other%20Poems'%C2%A0and%C2%A0%E2%80%98Nadir%20Godrej%20The%20Poet.'%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714548420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fbm7p3e2_godrej-family-_625x300_01_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeet-adi-godrej-and-his-brother-nadir-who-are-keeping-godrej-industries-after-split-5562493%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20ownership%20redistribution%2Cthe%20billion-dollar%20venture%20will%20now%20be%20splitinto%20two%20branches%20of%20the%20family.%20Adi%20and%20Nadir%20Godrej%20will%20maintain%20control%20of%20Godrej%20Industries%2C%20which%20includes%20five%20listed%20firms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeet-adi-godrej-and-his-brother-nadir-who-are-keeping-godrej-industries-after-split-5562493%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeet-adi-godrej-and-his-brother-nadir-who-are-keeping-godrej-industries