tional-award-winning-masterpiece%2Farticleshow%2F109748927.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Space%20Start-Up%20Uses%20Spy%20Satellite%20Tech%20To%20Track%20Mosquitos%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Indian%20start-up%20has%20modified%20sophisticated%20spy%20and%20surveillance%20satellite%20technology%20and%20tweaked%20it%20to%20detect%20mosquito%20breeding.%20Mosquitos%20are%20a%20menace%20of%20unparalleled%20proportions%20during%20the%20summer%20and%20monsoon%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMosquitos%20breed%20in%20water%20and%20are%20hard%20to%20detect%20using%20satellites%20and%20drones%2C%20but%20a%20Kolkatta-based%20space%20technology%20start-up%20called%20Sisir%20Radar%20has%20deployed%20high-end%20hyper-spectral%20imaging%20technology%20to%20be%20able%20to%20detect%20if%20containers%20and%20water%20bodies%20have%20mosquito%20larvae%20in%20them%20or%20not.%20The%20custom-made%20cameras%20were%20flown%20on%20drones.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F49crmed8_sisir-radar_625x300_01_May_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20finding%20Sisir%20Radar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BProud%20to%20share%20initial%20results%20of%20detection%20of%20mosquito%20larvae%2C%20through%20hyperspectral%20imaging.%20We%20planted%20clean%20water%20and%20larvae%20infested%20water%20in%20earthen%20and%20transparent%20plastic%20tumblers.%20Our%20drone-borne%20hyperspectral%20imager%20imaged%20them%20from%20a%20height%20of%2015%20metres%2C%20equivalent%20to%20the%20height%20of%20a%20five-storied%20block%20in%20Kolkata.%20%C2%A0We%20believe%20that%20this%20research%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20precisely%20identifying%20sources%20of%20mosquito%20larvae%20in%20water%20and%20insecticides%20can%20be%20sprayed%20in%20a%20measured%20manner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETapan%20Misra%2C%20better%20known%20as%20the%20father%20of%20India's%20spy%20satellites%20and%20former%20director%20of%20the%20ISRO's%20Space%20Applications%20Centre%2C%20Ahmedabad%20and%20founder%20of%20Sisir%20Radar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20present%20method%20of%20insecticide%20spraying%20is%20done%20arbitrarily%20and%20our%20water%20bodies%20and%20aquatic%20life%20forms%20are%20poisoned%20unnecessarily.%20Our%20research%20will%20help%20in%20not%20only%20eliminating%20the%20menace%20of%20mosquitoes%20at%20the%20larvae%20stage%20itself%2C%20benefitting%20our%20environment%20but%20also%20reducing%20the%20needless%20malaria%20and%20dengue%20deaths%20very%20significantly.%20It%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20globally%20250%20million%20people%20are%20afflicted%20with%20mosquito-borne%20diseases%20in%2085%20countries.%20Out%20of%20this%20humongous%20number%20of%20afflicted%20patients%2C%20around%20600%2C000%20die%20needlessly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Misra%2C%20known%20as%20a%20brilliant%20scientist%20with%20a%20huge%20command%20of%20synthetic%20aperture%20radar%20imaging%2C%20had%20a%20tumultuous%20career%20at%20ISRO%20and%20was%20summarily%20removed%20from%20his%20position%20as%20Director%20of%20the%20Space%20Applications%20Centre%20in%20July%202018.%20He%20made%20India's%20homemade%20spy%20satellites%20with%20day%20and%20night%20viewing%20capabilities%20leading%20the%20development%20of%20RISAT-1%20and%202.%20After%20retiring%20from%20ISRO%20he%20started%20Sisir%20Radar%20and%20his%20career%20path%20exemplifies%20age%20is%20no%20barrier%20for%20plunging%20to%20set%20up%20a%20startup.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Misra's%20life%20motto%20is%20%26quot%3Bcapturing%20the%20invisible%26quot%3B%20and%20now%20the%20same%20high-end%20remote%20sensing%20can%20also%20help%20in%20societal%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714547220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fs8d6d978_sisir-radar_625x300_01_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-space-start-up-uses-spy-satellite-tech-to-track-mosquitos-5563134%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indian%20start-up%20has%20modified%20sophisticated%20spy%20and%20surveillance%20satellite%20technology%20and%20tweaked%20it%20to%20detect%20mosquito%20breeding.%20Mosquitos%20are%20a%20menace%20of%20unparalleled%20proportions%20during%20the%20summer%20and%20monsoon%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-space-start-up-uses-spy-satellite-tech-to-track-mosquitos-5563134%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-space-start-up-uses-spy-satellite-tech-to-track-mosquitos-5563134%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-space-start-up-uses-spy-satellite-tech-to-track-mosquitos-5563134%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bomb%20threat%20traced%20back%20to%20domain%20'mail.ru'%3A%20Key%20pts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714546805000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109748733%2Cimgsize-179506.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fconfirmed-bomb-threat-mails-to-delhi-ncr-schools-originated-from-russia%2Farticleshow%2F109748680.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Email%20bomb%20threats%20to%20Delhi-NCR%20schools%2C%20traced%20to%20Russia%20via%20%26quot%3Bmail.ru%26quot%3B%2C%20create%20chaos%20in%2060%20schools%2C%20causing%20panic%20and%20disrupting%20school%20hours.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Close%20enough%20to%20see%20their%20faces'%3A