%20Hamilton%20Hall.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDozens%20of%20protesters%20were%20taken%20by%20police%20into%20busses%20in%20zip%20ties%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETensions%20have%20been%20rising%20between%20student%20protesters%20and%20authorities%20after%20days%20of%20protests%20on%20the%20Ivy%20League%20campus.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20Police%20Department%20officers%20in%20riot%20gear%20entered%20Columbia%20University's%20Hamilton%20Hall%20Tuesday%20evening%2C%20which%20had%20been%20occupied%20by%20protesters%20for%20roughly%2020%20hours%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20news%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Flive%2F2024%2F04%2F30%2Fnyregion%2Fcolumbia-protests-college%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20NYPD%20entered%20the%20building%20using%20a%20makeshift%20bridge%20that%20allowed%20them%20to%20climb%20into%20the%20second-story%20window.%20CNN%20reported%20that%20the%20NYPD%20said%20it%20had%20used%20%26quot%3Bdistraction%20devices%26quot%3B%20to%20disperse%20students%20but%20denied%20reports%20that%20tear%20gas%20was%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20protesters%20were%20taken%20by%20police%20into%20busses%20in%20zip%20ties%2C%20and%20as%20they%20were%20being%20bussed%20away%2C%20many%20chanted%2C%20%26quot%3BFree%20Palestine%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Times%20reported.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20university%20announced%20later%20in%20the%20evening%20that%20the%20building%20had%20been%20cleared%20of%20protesters%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bheightened%20activity%26quot%3B%20had%20concluded%2C%20per%20the%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideos%20from%20student%20groups%20on%20the%20scene%20show%20protesters%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FNationalSJP%2Fstatus%2F1785482293542301804%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epushed%20off%20campus%20by%20police%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Washington%20Post%20reported%20that%20some%20police%20entered%20the%20hall%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Feducation%2F2024%2F04%2F30%2Fcolumbia-university-protests-palestine-news%2F%23link-VTS5AUCISFFCRIX7EM65MIQUOU%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eguns%20drawn%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20requested%20that%20students%20shelter%20in%20place%20before%20police%20entered%20the%20campus%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudent%20groups%20had%20been%20demonstrating%20on%20campus%20for%20days%2C%20setting%20up%20tents%20and%20camping%20out%20at%20the%20Ivy%20League%20University%20to%20protest%20Israel's%20war%20on%20Gaza.%20Demands%20for%20the%20protest%20included%20that%20the%20university%20cut%20financial%20ties%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20university's%20%2413.6%20billion%20endowment%20includes%20investments%20in%20several%20weapons%20manufacturers%20and%20tech%20companies%20that%20do%20business%20with%20the%20Israeli%20government%2C%20which%20the%20student%20coalition%20Columbia%20University%20Apartheid%20Divest%20described%20as%20profiting%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20Israeli%20apartheid%2C%20genocide%2C%20and%20military%20occupation%20of%20Palestine%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F04%2F27%2Fbusiness%2Fcolumbia-history-divestment-student-protests%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20protesters%20entered%20Hamilton%20Hall%2C%20a%20humanities%20building%20on%20the%20university's%20Morningside%20Heights%20campus%2C%20and%20barricaded%20themselves%20indoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColumbia%20announced%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20students%20who%20occupied%20Hamilton%20Hall%20will%20face%20expulsion%2C%20while%20students%20who%20participated%20in%20encampments%20and%20refused%20to%20leave%20at%20the%20university's%20direction%20will%20face%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColumbia%20University%2C%20Columbia%20Students%20for%20Justice%20in%20Palestine%2C%20an