York%20institution%20with%20students%20staging%20a%20similar%20encampment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20an%20educator%20who%20has%20first%20hand%20experience%20with%20the%20over-policing%20of%20our%20schools%2C%20this%20is%20personal%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Bowman%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EI%20am%20outraged%20by%20the%20level%20of%20police%20presence%20called%20upon%20nonviolent%20student%20protestors%20on%20Columbia%20and%20CCNY%E2%80%99s%20campuses.%20As%20an%20educator%20who%20has%20first%20hand%20experience%20with%20the%20over-policing%20of%20our%20schools%2C%20this%20is%20personal%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Congressman%20Jamaal%20Bowman%20(%40RepBowman)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepBowman%2Fstatus%2F1785483005890355359%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ERep.%20Alexandria%20Ocasio-Cortez%20said%20that%20if%20students%20were%20hurt%20by%20the%20NYPD%2C%20the%20responsibility%20would%20fall%20on%20the%20university%20president%20and%20New%20York%20City%20Mayor%20Eric%20Adams%2C%20who%20expressed%20support%20for%20ending%20the%20encampments%20at%20Columbia%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOther%20leaders%20and%20schools%20have%20found%20a%20safe%2C%20de-escalatory%20path.%20This%20is%20the%20opposite%20of%20leadership%20and%20endangers%20public%20safety.%20A%20nightmare%20in%20the%20making%2C%26quot%3B%20Ocasio-Cortez%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FAOC%2Fstatus%2F1785476041089188198%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBowman%20and%20Ocasio-Cortez%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for