20in%20many%20cities%2C%20leading%20to%20severe%20dehydration.%20Doctors%20typically%20recommend%20an%20Oral%20Rehydration%20Salts%20(ORS)%20solution%20for%20diarrhoea%20and%20dehydration%2C%20especially%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347926%2Fcerelac-sugar-nestle-babies-infants-health-nutrition-report-meal-plan-for-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfants%20and%20children%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20Indian%20households%20are%20stocked%20up%20with%20packets%20of%20ORS%20solutions%2C%20and%20use%20them%20to%20beat%20the%20heat%2C%20also%20using%20it%20for%20children.%20Pharmacies%20are%20also%20stocked%20up%20with%20ORS%20solutions%20from%20different%20brands%2C%20available%20in%20different%20flavours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20bone%20of%20contention%20here%20is%2C%20are%20these%20real%20ORS%20solutions%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20ORS%20solution%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20getting%20into%20identifying%20what%E2%80%99s%20real%20and%20not%2C%20we%20first%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20purpose%20behind%20the%20creation%20of%20this%20life-saving%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20WHO%2C%20diarrhoea%20is%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20causes%20of%20death%20in%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%20five.%20Deaths%20due%20to%20diarrhoea%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoccur%20due%20to%20dehydration%2C%20which%20can%20be%20prevented%20by%20giving%20fluids%20at%20home%2C%20and%20in%20severe%20cases%2C%20ORS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EORS%20is%20a%20mixture%20of%20salt%20and%20sugar%20dissolved%20in%20water%20that%20can%20treat%20dehydration%20caused%20by%20diarrhoea%2C%20heat%20stroke%20or%20other%20illnesses%20where%20you%20lose%20a%20lot%20of%20fluid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsed%20since%201969%20by%20the%20WHO%20and%20UNICEF%2C%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20effective%20treatments%20for%20clinical%20dehydration%20across%20the%20world%2C%20which%20is%20cheap%20on%20the%20pocket%20too.%20It%20is%20recommended%20to%20treat%20dehydration%20across%20all%20age%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EORS%2C%20a%20balanced%20glucose-electrolyte%20mixture%2C%20is%20the%20name%20of%20the%20solution%20and%20is%20NOT%20the%20name%20of%20a%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20identify%20fake%20ORS%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20several%20news%20reports%20and%20warnings%20by%20the%20FSSAI%20to%20companies%20to%20stop%20printing%20misleading%20labels%20on%20energy%20drinks%20and%20calling%20them%20ORS.%20Yet%2C%20it%20continues%20as%20pharmacies%20are%20filled%20with%20energy%20drinks%20packaged%20as%20the%20solution%2C%20while%20it%20is%20just%20another%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevant%20Himatsingka%2C%20a%20health%20coach%20and%20content%20creator%2C%20who%20is%20on%20a%20crusade%20against%20such%20mislabelling%20and%20misinformation%2C%20has%20shared%20a%20new%20video%20where%20he%20explains%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327558%2Frevant-himatsingka-foodpharmer-shares-how-to-read-food-labels-for-health-risks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20identify%20real%20ORS%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20talks%20about%20the%20issues%20with%20fake%20ORS%20%E2%80%94%20primarily%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20has%20high%20sugar%20and%20%E2%80%98dangerously%20low%20sodium%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20also%20show%20that%20energy%20drinks%20disguised%20as%20ORS%20result%20in%20worsening%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20here%E2%80%99s%20how%20you%20can%20pick%20the%20right%20ORS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20correct%20ORS%20product%20will%20have%20%E2%80%98based%20on%20WHO%20formula%E2%80%99%20printed%20over%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhile%20real%20ORS%20is%20a%20drug%2C%20the%20fake%20ORS%20is%20just%20an%20energy%20drink%20that%20is%20regulated%20by%20the%20FSSAI.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20the%20ORS%20packet%20has%20an%20FSSAI%20sign%20on%20it%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20fake.%20If%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20sign%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20real%3B%20purchase%20it!%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6V8cEtrVEV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6V8cEtrVEV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6V8cEtrVEV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Revant%20Himatsingka%20(%40foodpharmer)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714463533000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348631%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20Indian%20households%20rely%20on%20Oral%20Rehydration%20Salts%20(ORS)%20solutions%20to%20combat%20dehydration%2C%20particularly%20during%20summer.%20But%20distinguishing%20real%20ORS%20from%20energy%20drinks%20marketed%20as%20such%20remains%20crucial.%20%E2%80%98Food%20pharmer%E2%80%99%20Revant%20Himatsingka%20shares%20how%20you%20can%20check%20real%20vs%20fake%20ORS.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348631%2Fors-fake-or-real-oral-rehydration-solution-for-summer-dehydration-diarrhoea-revant-food-pharmer%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Why%20Wait%20For%20Someone%2C%20Go%20Solo%E2%80%99%3A%20Ex-Banker%20is%20Taking%20Indian%20Women%20on%20Trips%20Across%20The%20World%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%20trekkers%20scaling%20the%20tranquil%20Dzuko%20Valley%20set%20amidst%20the%20highlands%20of%20Nagaland%20were%20treated%20to%20a%20fascinating%20sight.%20A%20group%20of%20girls%20could%20be%20seen%20cheering%20one%20among%20them%20as%20she%20trudged%20on.%20Closer%20inspection%20would%20reveal%20that%20their%20encouragement%20was%20directed%20towards%20a%20woman%20with%20an%20injured%20knee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20virgin%20landscape%20boasts%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Ftags%2Fbest-treks-in-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20challenging%20steep%20climb%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Meenakshi%20Singh%20was%20unsure%20whether%20her%20knee%20could%20bear%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20terrain.%20When%20she%20was%20inclined%20to%20back%20out%2C%20the%20girls%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20hear%20of%20it%3B%20amping%20her%20positivity%20with%20every%20step%20she%20took.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticulating%20this%20%E2%80%9Conce-in-a-lifetime%E2%80%9D%20experience%2C%20Meenakshi%20says%20the%20girls%20in%20her%20group%20never%20gave%20up%20on%20her.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20almost%20pulled%20me%20half-way!%20One%20of%20them%20was%20carrying%20my%20bag%2C%20another%20giving%20me%20water%20at%20every%20few%20stops%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20we%20made%20it%20to%20the%20finish%20point%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20group%20gathered%20around%20their%20hero%2C%20it%20was%20evident%20that%20this%20was%20a%20collective%20win.%20Cold%20water%20was%20relished%20at%20the%20top%20and%20biscuits%20were%20passed%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20day%2C%20the%20hills%20of%20Dzuko%20witnessed%20friendship%20at%20its%20best.%20And%20no%20one%20looking%20on%20would%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20that%20just%20a%20few%20days%20back%2C%20these%20girls%20had%20been%20strangers%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20what%20travel%20does%20to%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Zinal%20Doshi%2C%20leader%20of%20this%20iconic%20trek%20and%20founder%20of%20%E2%80%98The%20Flapper%20Life%E2%80%99.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334177%2Fbest-travel-startups-in-india-local-experiences-tentgram-curtain-call-adventures-not-on-map%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperiential%20travel%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20making%20solo%20travel%20possible%20for%20Indian%20women%2C%20arguably%20a%20tough%20feat%20to%20accomplish%2C%20according%20to%20Zinal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHelping%20women%20like%20Meenakshi%20realise%20their%20mettle%20is%20exactly%20what%20the%20Mumbai%20girl%20set%20out%20to%20do%20when%20she%20quit%20her%2014-year-long%20banking%20career%20to%20launch%20a%20travel%20startup%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20a%20venture%20that%20is%20breaking%20social%20constructs%20of%20solo%20travel%2C%20changing%20the%20status%20quo%20that%20once%20required%20women%20to%20have%20%E2%80%9Ccompany%20to%20feel%20safe%E2%80%9D%20and%20helping%20women%20not%20be%20so%20dismissive%20of%20themselves%2C%20is%20tough.%20But%20Zinal%20says%20there%20is%20fun%20in%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn