0itself.%20And%20no%20one%20wanted%20to%20resort%20to%20this%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20to%20this%20day%2C%20the%20safe%20lies%20untouched%20by%20the%20fingers%20of%20time%2C%20holding%20within%20it%20many%20mysteries%20and%20adding%20its%20own%20little%20bit%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344999%2Fhomestay-in-panchgani-roadtrip-from-mumbai-sustainable-organic-food-solar-panel-long-weekend-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintrigue%20to%20the%20property%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20attractive%20as%20it%20is%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20draw%20at%20the%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20homestay%20helmed%20by%20a%20mother-son%20duo%20from%20Delhi.%20The%20vibrant%20yellows%20of%20the%20bungalow%20are%20a%20sight%20for%20sore%20eyes%2C%20its%20layout%20offering%20pockets%20of%20unexpected%20calm%20to%20the%20weary%20traveller%20or%20to%20anyone%20who%20comes%20looking%20for%20some%20peace%20and%20quiet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWould%20you%20believe%20it%20if%20you%20were%20told%20that%20not%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20ago%2C%20this%20sprawling%20paradise%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccrumbling%20and%20dilapidated%20spot%E2%80%9D%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%2C%20and%20so%2C%20Siddarth%20settled%20down%20for%20a%20tete-a-tete%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20to%20unpeel%20the%20fascinating%20layers%20that%20lie%20beneath%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346785%2Fraison-detre-homestay-in-kullu-manali-near-beas-river-natural-spring-nitin-shalini-beri-sustainable%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20homestays%E2%80%99%20past%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fu