iri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTucked%20on%20a%20hillside%20with%20beautiful%20views%20on%20all%20sides%2C%20the%20land%20was%20a%20breath%20of%20fresh%20air.%20When%20we%20started%20designing%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20make%20it%20a%20homage%20to%20the%20tree.%20The%20tree%20has%20a%20magnificent%20presence%2C%20so%20the%20estate%20was%20named%20Paathiri%20after%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20George%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Epaathiri%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20Malayalam%20name%20for%20the%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisualising%20the%20layout%20of%20the%20place%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20property%20is%20situated%20on%20a%20hillside%2C%20our%20approach%20was%20to%20maximise%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291006%2Fbest-monsoon-treks-in-maharashtra-raigad-fort-kalsubai-karnala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epanoramic%20views%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20every%20room.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20we%20designed%20the%20layout%20in%20three%20levels.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20level%20encompasses%20the%20living%20room%2C%20dining%20area%2C%20kitchen%2C%20and%20master%20bedroom.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20level%20also%20features%20a%20sky%20deck%20that%20connects%20to%20the%20veranda%20on%20the%20second%20level%2C%20providing%20stunning%20views.%20The%20second%20level%2C%20positioned%20slightly%20lower%2C%20houses%20two%20additional%20bedrooms%20with%20skylit%20baths%20and%20a%20family%20living%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bridge%20connects%20this%20level%20to%20the%20first%2C%20which%20allows%20a%20seamless%20transition%20between%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20spaces.%20%E2%80%9CSurrounded%20by%20nature%2C%20the%20property%20also%20has%20a%20third%20level%20that%20includes%20a%20pool%2C%20gazebo%2C%20sky%20deck%2C%20lily%20pond%2C%20and%20dining%20deck%20area.%20This%20setup%20ensures%20that%20residents%20can%20enjoy%20a%20c